<section class="topic-section fade-up" id="t1">
  <div class="topic-header"><div class="topic-number">一</div><h2>古埃及人的精緻生活（愛美與享樂）</h2></div>
  <div class="topic-body">

    <div class="artifact">
      <div class="artifact-layout has-image">
        <div>
          <h3>化妝品盒子（眼線與眼影）</h3>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">📖 背後故事</span>
            <p>古埃及人非常愛美，但畫眼線不只是為了好看，更有<strong>實際用途</strong>：眼線可以吸收陽光，減少強烈紫外線對眼睛的刺激（類似現代美式足球員在眼底塗黑）。</p></div>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">🙏 宗教意義</span>
            <p>具有辟邪和宗教庇佑（<em class="en">religious protection</em>）的信念。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="artifact-images">
          <div class="artifact-img">
            <img src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/456857ef1876cd45c34e6033f8b819cd/352736ec-e277-43e8-9c20-4a16aee0e5f6/e8c5109b.png" alt="古埃及化妝品文物：鏡子與眼線用具" width="280" loading="lazy">
            <div class="img-caption">展覽文物：古埃及鏡子與化妝用具</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="artifact">
      <div class="artifact-layout has-image">
        <div>
          <h3>鏡子（生命之符 <em class="en">Ankh</em> 與女神）</h3>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">📖 背後故事</span>
            <p>在古埃及語中，「鏡子」與代表生命的「<em class="en">Ankh（生命之符）</em>」發音相同。鏡子手柄經常雕刻成 <em class="en">Hathor（哈索爾）</em>女神。</p></div>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">⭐ 女神小知識</span>
            <p><em class="en">Hathor</em> 是愛、美麗、音樂與舞蹈（<em class="en">love, beauty, music and dance</em>）的女神，特徵是擁有一對小牛耳。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="artifact-images">
          <div class="artifact-img">
            <img src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/456857ef1876cd45c34e6033f8b819cd/352736ec-e277-43e8-9c20-4a16aee0e5f6/830830b9.png" alt="生命之符Ankh圖示" width="280" loading="lazy">
            <div class="img-caption">生命之符 Ankh — 古埃及的生命象徵</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="artifact">
      <div class="artifact-layout has-image">
        <div>
          <h3><em class="en">Sistrum</em>（叉鈴／樂器）</h3>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">📖 背後故事</span>
            <p>真正的打擊樂器（<em class="en">percussion instrument</em>）文物，在祭神儀式（<em class="en">religious ritual</em>）和遊行時用來打拍子。</p></div>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">🔍 設計細節</span>
            <p>同樣刻有 <em class="en">Hathor</em> 女神頭像，上面帶有標誌性的小牛耳，因為所有享樂與藝術都歸她管。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="artifact-images">
          <div class="artifact-img">
            <img src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/456857ef1876cd45c34e6033f8b819cd/352736ec-e277-43e8-9c20-4a16aee0e5f6/c79a1d5c.png" alt="古埃及Sistrum叉鈴樂器" width="280" loading="lazy">
            <div class="img-caption">展覽文物：Sistrum 叉鈴</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="artifact">
      <div class="artifact-layout has-image">
        <div>
          <h3>廁所板</h3>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">💡 趣味小知識</span>
            <p>這件文物讓我們了解古埃及人的日常生活起居（<em class="en">daily life</em>）和宮廷衛生習慣，原來古代人一樣有衛生設施（<em class="en">sanitation facilities</em>）！</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="artifact-images">
          <div class="artifact-img">
            <img src="https://ppl-ai-code-interpreter-files.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/456857ef1876cd45c34e6033f8b819cd/352736ec-e277-43e8-9c20-4a16aee0e5f6/7a3a7c15.png" alt="古埃及廁所板與涼鞋文物" width="280" loading="lazy">
            <div class="img-caption">展覽文物：廁所板與涼鞋</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="topic-section fade-up" id="t2">
  <div class="topic-header"><div class="topic-number">二</div><h2>第一代 KOL 法老與平民王后</h2></div>
  <div class="topic-body">

    <div class="artifact">
      <div class="artifact-layout has-image">
        <div>
          <h3>阿蒙霍特普三世（<em class="en">Amenhotep III</em>）的婚姻聖甲蟲（<em class="en">Marriage Scarab</em>）</h3>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">👑 法老背景</span>
            <p>圖坦卡門（<em class="en">Tutankhamun</em>）的爺爺。他在位時國力鼎盛，作風國際化，娶了許多外國公主（<em class="en">foreign princesses</em>）。</p></div>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">😎 「霸道總裁」行為</span>
            <p>雖然有很多小妾，但法老只有一個正室。他為了向全國宣告自己娶了<strong>非王室貴族</strong>出身的泰伊（<em class="en">Tiye</em>）為大老婆，特別製作了幾十到上百隻「婚姻聖甲蟲」，在底部刻上公告（<em class="en">announcement</em>）到處派發。</p></div>
          <div class="callout">
            <span class="callout-icon">🐦</span>
