<section class="topic-section fade-up" id="t8">
  <div class="topic-header"><div class="topic-number">八</div><h2>古代畫家與音樂（日常生活延伸）</h2></div>
  <div class="topic-body">

    <div class="artifact">
      <div class="artifact-layout has-image">
        <div>
          <h3>畫家的調色板（<em class="en">Artist's Palette</em>）</h3>
          <div class="fact-block"><span class="fact-label">🎨 如何分辨文官與畫家？</span>
            <p>普通書記官（<em class="en">scribe</em>）寫字通常只用「紅、黑」兩種墨水（用蘆葦筆（<em class="en">reed pen</em>）書寫）。如果調色板（<em class="en">palette</em>）上有五、六種顏色，就一定是畫家的調色板。顏料（<em class="en">pigment</em>）是用礦石（<em class="en">minerals</em>）混合動物油脂或膠做成的。</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="artifact-images">
